    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>After running around in the Preferences dialog, the following is the location at which the highlight color for \"occurrences\" can be changed:</p>\n\n<p><code>General -&gt; Editors -&gt; Text Editors -&gt; Annotations</code></p>\n\n<p>Look for <code>Occurences</code> from the <em>Annotation types</em> list.</p>\n\n<p>Then, be sure that <code>Text as highlighted</code> is selected, then choose the desired color.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>And, a picture is worth a thousand words...</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/VlhJj.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/VlhJj.png\" alt=\"Preferences dialog\"></a><br>\n<sub>(source: <a href=\"http://coobird.net/img/eclipse-occurences-1.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\">coobird.net</a>)</sub>  </p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/0KACi.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/0KACi.png\" alt=\"Image showing occurences highlighted in orange.\"></a><br>\n<sub>(source: <a href=\"http://coobird.net/img/eclipse-occurences-2.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\">coobird.net</a>)</sub>  </p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7274,
      "reputation" : 8097,
      "user_id" : 12570,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 100,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/CUUVVWBr.jpg?s=256",
