    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>For those working in Titanium Studio, the item is a little different:  It's under the \"Titanium Studio\" Themes tab.</p>\n\n<p>The color to change is the \"Selection\" one in the top right.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/CxgI1.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n"
