    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>1 - right click the highlight whose color you want to change</p>\n\n<p>2 - select \"Properties\" in the popup menu</p>\n\n<p>3 - choose the new color (as <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/users/17172/coobird\">coobird</a> suggested)</p>\n\n<p>This solution is easy because you dont have to search for the highlight by its name (\"Ocurrence\" or \"Write Ocurrence\" etc), just right click and the appropriate window is shown.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3317838,
      "reputation" : 1106,
