    "body" : "<ol>\n<li><p>right click the highlight whose color you want to change</p></li>\n<li><p>select \"Preference\"</p></li>\n<li><p>->General->Editors->Text Editors->Annotations->Occurrences->Text as Hightlited->color.</p></li>\n<li><p>Select \"Preference ->java->Editor->Restore Defaults</p></li>\n</ol>\n"
