    "question_id" : 3434363,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>in my case (Eclipse IDE 2021-06), dark theme, the issue was with the background color of &quot;C/C++ Write Occurrences&quot;.</p>\n<p>On each click over a variable being written in the code, the editor highlights all occurrences of that variable.</p>\n<p>You can find this setting here:</p>\n<p>General -&gt; Editors -&gt; Text Editors -&gt; Annotations\nand then select 'C/C++ Write Occurrences'.\nAnd finally change che Color property.</p>\n"
  } ],
