  "body" : "<p>In eclipse, when your cursor is placed on a method (or other things), other places the method exists are highlighted. I'd like to change the color of this highlight, but after scouring the eclipse preferences many times in all 3 places, I have yet to find it.</p>\n<p>Any of you <code>Eclipse</code> gurus know where to find this option?</p>\n"
